label: Hermetschwil, Benediktinerinnenkloster, Cod. chart. 195

metadata.label: Summary (English)
metadata.value: This manuscript contains texts for the Liturgy of the Hours. It was probably created at Muri Abbey and was meant for the Hermetschwil nuns’ convent. Fol. 125v shows one of the few remaining prints of the “Teigdruck” (paste print) technique: Barbara with a palm branch and a tower.
